'''阿赫马托维奇反应'''是[[呋喃|呋喃]]转变为[[二氢吡喃|二氢吡喃]]环的过程，1971年由[[小奥斯曼·阿赫马托维奇|小奥斯曼·阿赫马托维奇]]发现。<ref>''Synthesis of methyl 2,3-dideoxy--alk-2-enopyranosides from furan compounds : A general approach to the total synthesis of monosaccharides'' [[Tetrahedron|Tetrahedron]], Volume 27, Issue 10, '''1971''', Pages 1973-1996 O. Achmatowicz, P. Bukowski, B. Szechner, Z. Zwierzchowska and A. Zamojski {{DOI|10.1016/S0040-4020(01)98229-8}}</ref> 最初方法是用[[糠醇|糠醇]]与[[溴|溴]]在[[甲醇|甲醇]]中反应，先得到2,5-二甲氧基-[[二氢糠醇|二氢糠醇]]，它用稀[[硫酸|硫酸]]发生[[重排|重排]]便得到一个二氢吡喃衍生物。该衍生物与[[原甲酸甲酯|原甲酸甲酯]]和[[三氟化硼|三氟化硼]]反应上甲基[[保护基|保护基]]，接着用[[硼氢化钠|硼氢化钠]]还原[[酮|酮]]基，可得另一二氢吡喃衍生物，这个产物可用作许多[[单糖|单糖]]的合成中间体。

[[File:The_Achmatowicz_reaction.svg|600px]]

这个反应用于天然产物''desoxoprosophylline''<ref>''Asymmetric total synthesis of (+)-desoxoprosophylline'' [[Tetrahedron_Letters|Tetrahedron Letters]], Volume 39, Issue 50, 10 December '''1998''', Pages 9227-9228 Cui-Fen Yang, Yi-Ming Xu, Li-Xin Liao and Wei-Shan Zhou {{DOI|10.1016/S0040-4039(98)02129-7}} </ref>、[[核球壳菌素|核球壳菌素]]（''Pyrenophorin''）<ref>''Efficient Conditions for Conversion of 2-Substituted Furans into 4-Oxygenated 2-Enoic Acids and Its Application to Synthesis of (+)-Aspicilin, (+)-Patulolide A, and (-)-Pyrenophorin''  Kobayashi, Y.; Nakano, M.; Kumar, G. B.; Kishihara, K. [[J._Org._Chem.|J. Org. Chem.]]; (Article); '''1998'''; 63(21); 7505-7515.  {{DOI|10.1021/jo980942a}} </ref>和[[包公藤甲素|包公藤甲素]]（''Bao Gong Teng A''）<ref>''Organometallic Enantiomeric Scaffolding: Organometallic Chirons. Total Synthesis of (-)-Bao Gong Teng A by a Molybdenum-Mediated [5+2] Cycloaddition''
Yongqiang Zhang and Lanny S. Liebeskind [[J._Am._Chem._Soc.|J. Am. Chem. Soc.]] '''2006'''; 128(2) pp 465 - 472; (Article) {{DOI|10.1021/ja055623x}}</ref> 和[[全合成|全合成]]中。

最近也用于[[定向多样性合成|定向多样性合成]] <ref>''A Synthesis Strategy Yielding Skeletally Diverse Small Molecules Combinatorially'' 
Martin D. Burke, Eric M. Berger, and Stuart L. Schreiber [[J._Am._Chem._Soc.|J. Am. Chem. Soc.]] 126 (43), 14095 -14104, '''2004'''. {{DOI|10.1021/ja0457415}} </ref> <ref>试剂为：[[N-溴代琥珀酰亚胺|NBS]]、[[对甲苯磺酸吡啶鎓盐|PPTS]]。另见[[固相合成|固相合成]]。</ref> 

[[File:AchmatowiczBurke2006.svg|600px]]

以及 enantiomeric scaffolding 中。<ref>''Practical, Scalable, High-Throughput Approaches to 3-Pyranyl and 3-Pyridinyl Organometallic Enantiomeric Scaffolds Using the Achmatowicz Reaction'' Thomas C. Coombs, Maurice D. Lee, IV, Heilam Wong, Matthew Armstrong, Bo Cheng, Wenyong Chen, Alessandro F. Moretto, and Lanny S. Liebeskind [[J._Org._Chem.|J. Org. Chem.]] 73 (3), 882 -888, '''2008'''. {{DOI|10.1021/jo702006z}}</ref><ref>过程为：[[氯甲酸苄酯|氯甲酸苄酯]]为胺上[[Cbz|Cbz]]保护基；[[mCPBA|mCPBA]]促进的阿赫马托维奇反应；与[[钼|钼]]的配位。Cp=[[环戊二烯|环戊二烯]]基。</ref>

